Maar ik ben geen koning.
Ik ben slechts je zoon.

457
00:36:12.873 --> 00:36:13.873
Obasi.

458
00:36:14.873 --> 00:36:16.123
Chigaru.

459
00:36:16.290 --> 00:36:17.290
Obasi.

460
00:36:17.873 --> 00:36:21.623
